ingredients: WATER & CLAM JUICE, TEXTURIZED VEGETABLE PROTEIN (SOY FLOUR), BREADING (ENRICHED UNBLEACHED FLOUR(WHEAT FLOUR, MALTED BARLEY FLOUR, NIACIN, FERROUS SULFATE, THIAMINE, MONOITRATE, RIBOFLAVIN, FOLIC ACID)), WATER, CONTAINS 2% OR LESS OF THE FOLLOWING: SOYBEAN OIL, YEAST, SALT, DEGERMINATED YELLOW CORNMEAL, SUGAR, DOUGH CONDITIONER (ASCORBIC ACID, DEXTROSE, ENZYMES, SUNFLOWER OIL), CALCIUM PROPIONATE [TO RETAIN FRESHNESS], MARGARINE (VEGETABLE OIL, SOYBEAN OIL, PALM OIL, AND/OR FULLY HYDROGENATED SOYBEAN OIL), WATER, SALT, MONO AND DIGLYCERIDES, SOY LECITHIN, POTASSIUM SORBATE AND SODIUM BENZOATE PRESERVATIVES), ARTIFICIAL BUTTER FLAVOR, COLORED WITH BETA CAROTENE, VITAMIN A PALMITATE, ADDED, CHOURICO (PORK, VINEGAR, NONFAT DRY MILK, SALT, PAPRIKA, WINE, FLAVORINGS, SPICES, SODIUM NITRATE, BEEF CASINGS), CELERY, ONION, RED AND GREEN BELL PEPPERS, SALT, CLAM MEAT, CHEESE BLEND (PASTEURIZED MILK CULTURES, SLT ENZYMES), IMITATION BACON BITS (SOY FLOUR, SOYBEAN OIL, SALT, LESS THAN 2% OF HYDROLYZED SOY PROTEIN, YEAST EXTRACT, NATURAL SMOKE FLAVOR, SUNFLOWER OIL, SUGAR, DEXTROSE, INACTIVE DRIED YEAST CARAMEL COLOR, RED #3, HYDROLYZED SOY AND CORN PROTEIN, SOY LECITHIN AND NATURAL FLAVOR), PEPPER, GARLIC, SPICES, PAPRIKA, PARSLEY.
